title: Valley of the Sun Stage Race
Focus Grand Prix
description: Focus Grand Prix Criterium is a 0.7 mile circuit located at the SanTan Autoplex, Gilbert, Arizona.
course: Start/Finish is on Speedway Drive, circulating counter-clockwise on a \"D\" shaped loop on Motorplex Loop.  Also hosting a \"High Noon\" 200 meter drag race showdown.
registration: Registration is Day-Of starting at 6:30am, closing 30 minutes prior to applicable races.  Juniors $5, All others $30.  Three cans on non-perishable food qualifies for a second race!!  Proceeds benefiting the Gilbert Open Arms Care Center.  Drag Race $5 per entrant.
notes: Parking is limited for this event.  Please carpool with your teammates.  Teams please set up EZUps on perimeter sidewalks.
directions: From the South East Valley Loop 202, exit on Val Vista Rd.  Val Vista north to Market Street, then left.  Left or Right on Motorplex Loop takes you to either side of the race course.
